<eesti>Eranditaotluse esitamise kord </eesti>
<inglise>Procedure for Submission of Applications for Exemption </inglise>
<eesti>Rahandusministri 11. septembri 2001. a m&auml;&auml;rus nr 79 </eesti>
<inglise>Regulation No. 79 of the Minister of Finance of 11 September 2001 </inglise>
<eesti>(RTL 2001, 109, 1516) </eesti>
<inglise>(RTL (1) 2001, 109, 1516), </inglise>
<eesti>j&otilde;ustunud 1. oktoobril 2001. a. </eesti>
<inglise>entered into force 1 October 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;&auml;rus kehtestatakse "Konkurentsiseaduse" (RT I 2001, 56, 332) &sect; 10 l&otilde;ike 1 alusel. </eesti>
<inglise>This Regulation is established on the basis of subsection 10 (1) of the Competition Act (RT (2) I 2001, 56, 332). </inglise>
<eesti>1. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 1 </inglise>
<eesti>&Uuml;lds&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise>General Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 1. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 1. </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;&auml;ruses s&auml;testatakse n&otilde;uded eranditaotlusele (edaspidi taotlus), erandi kehtivuse t&auml;htaja pikendamiseks esitatavale taotlusele ja taotluse esitamise kord. </eesti>
<inglise>This Regulation provides the requirements for applications for exemption (hereinafter applications), the requirements for applications for extension of the term of an exemption, and the procedure for submission of applications. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 2. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 2. </inglise>
<eesti>Erandi saamiseks tuleb Konkurentsiametile esitada taotlus enne konkurentsi kahjustava kokkuleppe s&otilde;lmimist, koosk&otilde;lastatud tegevuse alustamist v&otilde;i otsuse vastuv&otilde;tmist (edaspidi kokkulepe, tegevus v&otilde;i otsus) v&otilde;i kuue kuu jooksul erandit vajava kokkuleppe s&otilde;lmimisest, tegevuse alustamisest v&otilde;i otsuse vastuv&otilde;tmisest arvates. </eesti>
<inglise>In order to obtain an exemption, an application shall be submitted to the Competition Board before entry into an agreement, commencement of concerted practices or adoption of a decision restricting competition (hereinafter agreement, practices or decision) or within six months as of entry into an agreement, commencement of practices or adoption of a decision which requires an exemption. </inglise>
<eesti>Vastav kokkulepe v&otilde;i otsus v&otilde;i nende konkurentsi kahjustav osa on kuni erandi andmiseni kehtetu. </eesti>
<inglise>Such agreement or decision or a part thereof which restricts competition is invalid until the grant of the exemption. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 3. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 3. </inglise>
<eesti>Taotlus kokkuleppe, otsuse v&otilde;i nende osa v&otilde;i tegevuse kohta, mis ei olnud kokkuleppe s&otilde;lmimisel, tegevuse alustamisel v&otilde;i otsuse vastuv&otilde;tmisel konkurentsiseadusega vastuolus, tuleb esitada kolme kuu jooksul, alates asjaolude ilmnemisest, mille t&otilde;ttu kokkulepe v&otilde;i otsus v&otilde;i selle osa v&otilde;i tegevus osutub konkurentsiseadusega vastuolus olevaks, v&otilde;i ajast, millal nende olemasolust oleks pidanud teada saama. </eesti>
<inglise>An application with regard to an agreement, a decision or a part thereof or practices which was not in conflict with the Competition Act upon entry into the agreement, commencement of the practices or adoption of the decision shall be submitted within three months as of the appearance of circumstances due to which the agreement or decision or a part thereof or the practices becomes contrary to the Competition Act or within three months as of the time such circumstances should have become evident. </inglise>
<eesti>Vastav kokkulepe v&otilde;i otsus v&otilde;i selle osa on vastavate asjaolude ilmnemisest kuni erandi andmiseni kehtetu. </eesti>
<inglise>Such agreement or decision or a part thereof is invalid from the appearance of the circumstances until the grant of the exemption. </inglise>
<eesti>2. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 2 </inglise>
<eesti>Taotlusele esitatavad n&otilde;uded </eesti>
<inglise>Requirements for Applications </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 4. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 4. </inglise>
<eesti>Taotluses esitatakse ettev&otilde;tjate kohta j&auml;rgmised andmed: </eesti>
<inglise>The following information concerning an undertaking shall be presented in an application: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kokkuleppes, tegevuses v&otilde;i otsuses osalevate ja nendega seotud ettev&otilde;tjate iseloomustus; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the characteristics of undertakings which participate in the agreement, practices or decision or of undertakings connected thereto; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kokkuleppes, tegevuses v&otilde;i otsuses osalevate ettev&otilde;tjate &auml;rinimed, registrikoodid, aadressid, sidevahendite (telefon, faks jne) numbrid; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the business names, registry codes, addresses and telecommunications numbers (telephone, facsimile, etc.) of undertakings which participate in the agreement, practices or decision; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kokkuleppes, tegevuses v&otilde;i otsuses osalevate ettev&otilde;tjatega seotud ja m&auml;&auml;ratletud kaubaturul tegutsevate ettev&otilde;tjate &auml;rinimed, registrikoodid, aadressid, sidevahendite (telefon, faks jne) numbrid; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the business names, registry codes, addresses and telecommunications numbers (telephone, facsimile, etc.) of undertakings which operate in the specified product market and are connected to the undertakings which participate in the agreement, practices or decision; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kokkuleppes, tegevuses v&otilde;i otsuses osalevate ettev&otilde;tjate omandisuhted ja aktsiate v&otilde;i osade omanike nimed; </eesti>
<inglise>4) the ownership relations of undertakings which participate in the agreement, practices or decision and the names of the shareholders; </inglise>
<eesti>5) kokkuleppes, tegevuses v&otilde;i otsuses osalevate ettev&otilde;tjate tegevusalad. </eesti>
<inglise>5) the areas of activity of the undertakings which participate in the agreement, practices or decision. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 5. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 5. </inglise>
<eesti>Taotluses esitatakse kokkuleppe, tegevuse v&otilde;i otsuse kohta j&auml;rgmised andmed: </eesti>
<inglise>The following information concerning the agreement, practices or decision shall be submitted in an application: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kokkuleppe, tegevuse v&otilde;i otsuse sisu ja eesm&auml;rk; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the content and objectives of the agreement, practices or decision; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kokkuleppe v&otilde;i otsuse iga punkti, mille tagaj&auml;rjeks on v&otilde;i v&otilde;ib olla konkurentsi kahjustamine, nimetamine koos viitamisega "Konkurentsiseaduse" &sect;-i 4 l&otilde;ike 1 vastavale punktile. </eesti>
<inglise>2) a description of each point of the agreement or decision which results or may result in the restriction of competition and a reference to the relevant clause of subsection 4 (1) of the Competition Act. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 6. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 6. </inglise>
<eesti>Kokkuleppest, tegevusest v&otilde;i otsusest m&otilde;jutatud kaubaturu kohta esitatakse: </eesti>
<inglise>The following shall be submitted concerning a product market influenced by the agreement, practices or decision: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kokkuleppest, tegevusest v&otilde;i otsusest m&otilde;jutatud kaubaturu (edaspidi kaubaturg) m&auml;&auml;ratlemise aluseks olevad kaubad ja sellise valiku p&otilde;hjendus; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the products which are the basis for determination of the product market influenced by the agreement, practices or decision (hereinafter product market) and the reasoning behind the choice; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kokkuleppest, tegevusest v&otilde;i otsusest m&otilde;jutatud kaupade k&auml;ibimise ala (Eesti territoorium v&otilde;i selle osa) ning k&auml;ive nimetatud alal; </eesti>
<inglise>2) the area in which the products influenced by the agreement, practices or decision are circulated (the territory of Estonia or a part thereof) and the turnover in that area; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kokkuleppes, tegevuses v&otilde;i otsuses osalevate ja nendega seotud ettev&otilde;tjate eelmise majandusaasta kaupade realiseerimise netok&auml;ive; </eesti>
<inglise>3) the realised net turnover of goods during the previous financial year for undertakings which participate in the agreement, practices or decision and for undertakings connected thereto; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kokkuleppes, tegevuses v&otilde;i otsuses osalevate ettev&otilde;tjate ja konkurentide osat&auml;htsuse m&auml;&auml;ratlus kaubaturul; </eesti>
<inglise>4) specification of the share of the relative importance in the product market of undertakings which participate in the agreement, practices or decision and of their competitors; </inglise>
<eesti>5) erandit taotlevate ettev&otilde;tjate ja &sect; 4 punktis 3 loetletud ettev&otilde;tjate (kontserni) rahaline ja koguseline turuosa protsentides vastaval kaubaturul Eesti territooriumil v&otilde;i selle osal; </eesti>
<inglise>5) the percentage market share in terms of money and volume held by the undertakings applying for the exemption and by undertakings specified in clause 4 3) (a group) in the relevant product market across the territory of Estonia or in a part thereof; </inglise>
<eesti>6) informatsioon konkurentide ja nende turuosa kohta; </eesti>
<inglise>6) information on competitors and their market share; </inglise>
<eesti>7) tegurid, mis m&otilde;jutavad teiste ettev&otilde;tjate p&auml;&auml;su m&auml;&auml;ratletud kaubaturule (n&auml;iteks tooraine k&auml;ttesaadavus, load, litsentsid, tarbijate eelistused). </eesti>
<inglise>7) factors which influence the access of other undertakings to the product market (for example accessibility of raw materials, permits, licences, consumer preferences). </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 7. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 7. </inglise>
<eesti>Erandi taotlemise p&otilde;hjenduste kohta esitatakse j&auml;rgmine teave: </eesti>
<inglise>The following information shall be submitted concerning the reasoning behind applying for an exemption: </inglise>
<eesti>1) kuidas kokkulepe, tegevus v&otilde;i otsus aitab kaasa teenindamise v&otilde;i kaupade tootmise v&otilde;i levitamise parandamisele, keskkonna kaitsmisele v&otilde;i tehnilise v&otilde;i majandusliku progressi edendamisele; </eesti>
<inglise>1) how the agreement, practices or decision contribute to improving the supply of services or the production or distribution of goods, protecting the environment or promoting technical or economic progress; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kuidas kokkulepe, tegevus v&otilde;i otsus v&otilde;imaldab tarbijatel saada sellest tulenevast kasust &otilde;iglast osa; </eesti>
<inglise>2) how the agreement, practices or decision allow consumers a fair share of the resulting benefit; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kas kokkulepe, tegevus v&otilde;i otsus ei too kolmandatele isikutele kaasa kitsendusi, mis ei ole h&auml;davajalikud punktis 1 nimetatud eesm&auml;rkide saavutamisel ja ei p&otilde;hjusta olulist konkurentsi kahjustamist kaubaturul. </eesti>
<inglise>3) whether the agreement, practices or decision bring about restrictions on third parties which are not indispensable to the attainment of the objectives specified in clause 1) and do not cause significant restrictions on competition in the product market. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 8. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 8. </inglise>
<eesti>Erandi kehtivuse t&auml;htaja pikendamiseks esitatavale taotlusele kehtivad &sect;-des 4-7 kehtestatud n&otilde;uded. </eesti>
<inglise>The requirements established in &sect;&sect; 4-7 apply to applications to extend the term of an exemption. </inglise>
<eesti>Konkurentsiameti peadirektor v&otilde;i tema aset&auml;itja v&otilde;ib vabastada erandi taotluse pikendamisel ettev&otilde;tja osaliselt v&otilde;i t&auml;ielikult &sect;-des 4-7 nimetatud andmete ja teabe esitamisest, kui esialgses taotluses esitatud andmed ja teave ei ole muutunud. </eesti>
<inglise>The Director General of the Competition Board or his or her deputy may, in whole or in part, release an undertaking applying for extension of an exemption from submitting the information specified in &sect;&sect; 4-7 if the information submitted in the initial application has not changed. </inglise>
<eesti>3. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 3 </inglise>
<eesti>Taotluse esitamine </eesti>
<inglise>Submission of application </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 9. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 9. </inglise>
<eesti>Taotluse esitavad kokkuleppe s&otilde;lminud v&otilde;i koosk&otilde;lastatult tegutsenud v&otilde;i otsuse vastuv&otilde;tnud ettev&otilde;tjad &uuml;hiselt v&otilde;i &uuml;ks nendest. </eesti>
<inglise>An application shall be submitted jointly by the undertakings which entered into an agreement, engaged in concerted practices or adopted a decision, or by one of such undertakings. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 10. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 10. </inglise>
<eesti>Taotluse esitajad v&otilde;ivad &uuml;hiselt v&otilde;i eraldi eranditaotluse tagasi v&otilde;tta igal ajal kuni erandi andmiseni, esitades sellekohase kirjaliku avalduse, kusjuures nimetatud avalduse esitaja ei pea olema sama isik, kes taotluse esitas. </eesti>
<inglise>Applicants may withdraw an application for exemption jointly or separately at any time before the grant of the exemption by submitting a corresponding written petition, and the person submitting the petition need not be the same as the person who submitted the application. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 11. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 11. </inglise>
<eesti>Konkurentsiameti n&otilde;udmisel peab taotluse esitaja andma taotluses sisalduvate andmete ja teabe kohta selgitusi ning esitama Konkurentsiameti n&otilde;udel tutvumiseks dokumentide originaalid v&otilde;i nende koopiad, mille originaalile vastavust kinnitab nende esitaja oma allkirjaga. </eesti>
<inglise>At the request of the Competition Board, an applicant shall provide explanations concerning the information contained in the application and submit for examination original documents or true copies thereof, certified by the signature of the person submitting the copies. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 12. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 12. </inglise>
<eesti>Kui taotluses sisalduv v&otilde;i sellega seoses esitatud teave on mittet&auml;ielik, eba&otilde;ige v&otilde;i eksitav, n&otilde;uab Konkurentsiamet kogu teabe esitamist ja m&auml;&auml;rab selleks t&auml;htaja. </eesti>
<inglise>If information contained in an application or information relating to the application is incomplete, incorrect or misleading, the Competition Board shall demand submission of all the information and set a deadline for submission thereof. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 13. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 13. </inglise>
<eesti>Esitatud andmete olulistest muudatustest peab Konkurentsiametit teavitama v&auml;hemalt seitsme p&auml;eva jooksul vastava teabe saamisest. </eesti>
<inglise>The Competition Board shall be informed of any substantial changes in the information submitted within seven days as of receipt of the corresponding information. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 14. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 14. </inglise>
<eesti>&Auml;risaladuseks peetavale teabele lisatakse vastav m&auml;rge v&otilde;i esitatakse vastava m&auml;rkega eraldi lisa. </eesti>
<inglise>A corresponding notation shall be annexed to information deemed to be a business secret or a separate annex shall be submitted bearing the corresponding notation. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 15. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 15. </inglise>
<eesti>Konkurentsiameti peadirektor v&otilde;i tema aset&auml;itja v&otilde;ib anda erandi kuni viieks aastaks. </eesti>
<inglise>The Director General of the Competition Board or his or her deputy may grant an exemption for up to five years. </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;&auml;ratud t&auml;htaja l&otilde;ppemisel v&otilde;ib erandi saanud isik(ud) esitada v&auml;hemalt kuus kuud enne otsuses toodud erandi kehtivuse t&auml;htaja l&otilde;ppemist taotluse erandi kehtivuse t&auml;htaja pikendamiseks. </eesti>
<inglise>Upon termination of the term, the person(s) who was (were) granted an exemption may submit an application for extension of the term of the exemption at least six months before the termination of the term of the exemption as indicated in the decision. </inglise>
<eesti>Erandi kehtivuse t&auml;htaega pikendatakse erandi andmise otsusega. </eesti>
<inglise>The term of an exemption shall be extended by a decision to grant an exemption. </inglise>
<eesti>4. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 4 </inglise>
<eesti>Taotluse lisad </eesti>
<inglise>Annexes to Applications </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 16. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 16. </inglise>
<eesti>Taotluse lisadena tulevad esitada koopiad j&auml;rgmistest dokumentidest: </eesti>
<inglise>Copies of the following documents shall be submitted as annexes to an application: </inglise>
<eesti>1) dokumendid, mis olid aluseks kaubaturu m&auml;&auml;ratlemisel; </eesti>
<inglise>1) the documents which were the basis upon determination of the product market; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kokkuleppe, tegevuse v&otilde;i otsuse k&otilde;igi poolte eelnenud majandusaasta aruannete koopiad koos lisadega; </eesti>
<inglise>2) copies of the annual reports for the previous financial year of all the parties to the agreement, practices or decision, and the annexes thereto; </inglise>
<eesti>3) koopiad anal&uuml;&uuml;sidest v&otilde;i arvamustest, mis on ette valmistatud seoses kokkuleppele, tegevusele v&otilde;i otsusele erandi saamiseks v&otilde;i mis on taotluseks esitatavate andmete allikaks; </eesti>
<inglise>3) copies of analyses or opinions which were prepared in connection with obtaining an exemption for the agreement, practices or decision or which are the source of information submitted in the application; </inglise>
<eesti>4) kokkuleppe v&otilde;i otsuse projekti l&otilde;pliku variandi koopia (kui taotlus esitatakse enne kokkuleppe s&otilde;lmimist v&otilde;i otsuse vastuv&otilde;tmist) v&otilde;i allakirjutatud kokkuleppe v&otilde;i vastuv&otilde;etud otsuse koopia (kui taotlus esitatakse p&auml;rast kokkuleppe allakirjutamist v&otilde;i otsuse vastuv&otilde;tmist); </eesti>
<inglise>4) a copy of the agreement or the final version of the draft decision (if the application is submitted before entry into the agreement or adoption of the decision) or a copy of the signed agreement or adopted decision (if the application is submitted after the agreement is signed or the decision adopted); </inglise>
<eesti>5) dokument riigil&otilde;ivu tasumise kohta. </eesti>
<inglise>5) a document certifying the payment of the state fee. </inglise>
<eesti>5. peat&uuml;kk </eesti>
<inglise>Chapter 5 </inglise>
<eesti>Rakenduss&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise>Implementing Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 17. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 17. </inglise>
<eesti>Rahandusministri 24. septembri 1998. a m&auml;&auml;rus nr 79 "Eranditaotluse esitamise juhendi kinnitamine" (RTL 1998, 292/293, 1191) tunnistatakse kehtetuks. </eesti>
<inglise>Regulation no. 79 of the Minister of Finance of 24 September 1998 "Approval of Instructions for Submission of Applications for Exemptions" (RTL 1998, 292/293, 1191) is repealed. </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 18. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 18. This Regulation enters into force on 1 October 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>M&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub 2001. aasta 1. oktoobril. </eesti>
